1 I've told you this so you won't give up your trust in me. 2 They will expel you from
the synagogues—in fact the time is coming when those who kill you will think they
are doing God a service. 3 They'll do this because they have never known the Father
or me. I've told you this so that when these things happen, you'll remember what I
told you. 4 I didn't need to tell you this right at the beginning because I was going to
be with you. 5 But now I'm going to the one who sent me, and yet not one of you is
