12 There's much more I want to explain to you, but you couldn't stand it now.
13 However, when the Spirit of truth comes, he will teach you the whole truth. He
doesn't speak for himself, but he only says what he hears, and he will tell you what's
going to happen. 14 He brings me glory for he teaches you whatever he receives from
me. 15 All that belongs to the Father is mine. This is why I said that the Spirit teaches
