to you in this short letter. 23 You should know that Timothy has been set free. If he gets
here soon, I will come with him to see you. 24 Give my greetings to all your leaders,
and to all the believers there. The believers here in Italy send their greetings. 25 May
God's grace be with all of you. Amen.
