19 Those I love I correct and discipline. So be really sincere, and repent. 20 Look,
I'm standing at the door, knocking. If anyone hears me calling and opens the door,
I will come in and eat with them, and they with me. 21 I will have those who are
victorious sit down with me beside my throne, just as I was victorious and sat down
beside my Father on his throne. 22 If you have ears, listen to what the Spirit is telling
